msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "Mozilla Foundation Incubator"
msgstr "Incubator da Fundação Mozilla"

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "Mozilla Foundation Incubator"
msgstr "Incubator da Fundação Mozilla"

msgctxt "title"
msgid "Mozilla Foundation Incubator"
msgstr "Incubator da Fundação Mozilla"

msgctxt "hero_title"
msgid "Mozilla Foundation Incubator"
msgstr "Incubator da Fundação Mozilla"

msgctxt "hero_description"
msgid "Bridging a critical gap in funding to help values-driven tech thrive"
msgstr "Preencher uma lacuna crítica de financiamento para ajudar a tecnologia orientada por valores a prosperar."

msgctxt "hero_image_alt_text"
msgid "A group of people sitting in a circle"
msgstr "Um grupo de pessoas sentadas em círculo"

msgctxt "body.aca37199-56c7-4923-992a-992f6115d4eb.left_column.d7860eef-f1e9-4840-a6f7-c41a257e1068"
msgid ""
"<b>Mozilla Foundation believes that better tech futures are possible—and we're proving it by investing in projects that will make them real.</b> We back technologists that are building alternatives "
"that work—tools that are open, transparent, and designed to serve everyone. We support technologies that give power back to people and communities, and we plant seeds of radical change by funding "
"projects that push forward new tech paradigms."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.aca37199-56c7-4923-992a-992f6115d4eb.left_column.d7860eef-f1e9-4840-a6f7-c41a257e1068"
msgid ""
"<b>Mozilla Foundation’s Incubator is a catalyst for this movement.</b> All too often, promising alternatives launch, but fail to bridge the “valley of death” between prototyping and sustainability. "
"We help build a community around promising ideas, finding the right users, contributors, mentors, and funders to sustain the work of technologists without compromising their values. We call this "
"“product-community fit.”"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.aca37199-56c7-4923-992a-992f6115d4eb.left_column.d7860eef-f1e9-4840-a6f7-c41a257e1068"
msgid ""
"Every sustainable alternative we help build becomes proof that technology can work differently. By helping viable alternatives reach their full potential, <b>we change what's possible: one "
"successful alternative at a time.</b>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.aca37199-56c7-4923-992a-992f6115d4eb.right_column.96fb875a-1436-42b0-8e54-328db18d7329.quote"
msgid "While traditional funding optimizes for profit, we invest in technologies that put people first."
msgstr "Enquanto o financiamento tradicional visa o lucro, nós investimos em tecnologias que priorizam as pessoas."

msgctxt "body.aca37199-56c7-4923-992a-992f6115d4eb.right_column.96fb875a-1436-42b0-8e54-328db18d7329.attribution"
msgid "Lindsey Dodson, Director of Global Grants"
msgstr "Lindsey Dodson, Diretora de Subsídios Globais"

msgctxt "body.a2e9bb02-54c9-4b30-b8df-6fd8b57a39de.title"
msgid "Incubator Cohorts"
msgstr "Coortes do Incubator"

msgctxt "body.176943fd-e59c-48b2-a261-7e12f698e44d.right_column.1ae0d6b9-a307-49c2-b942-55ac8ccd1219"
msgid "Democracy x AI cohort"
msgstr "Democracia x AI cohort"

msgctxt "body.176943fd-e59c-48b2-a261-7e12f698e44d.right_column.1ae0d6b9-a307-49c2-b942-55ac8ccd1219"
msgid "We believe that a better, more democratic tech future isn’t just possible—it’s still ours to build."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.176943fd-e59c-48b2-a261-7e12f698e44d.right_column.1ae0d6b9-a307-49c2-b942-55ac8ccd1219"
msgid ""
"Technology has always tested and shaped democratic life, and today, AI is reshaping societies faster than democratic institutions can adapt. But this isn’t just about AI—it’s about power: who gets "
"it, and who has a say in how it shapes democracy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.176943fd-e59c-48b2-a261-7e12f698e44d.right_column.1ae0d6b9-a307-49c2-b942-55ac8ccd1219"
msgid ""
"Our Democracy x AI cohort is made up of technologists who are building tech alternatives that give power back to people and communities, turning imagination into infrastructure for resistance, "
"reinvention, and renewal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.176943fd-e59c-48b2-a261-7e12f698e44d.right_column.1ae0d6b9-a307-49c2-b942-55ac8ccd1219"
msgid "The Democracy x AI cohort will be announced soon. Stay tuned to meet the people and projects imagining—and building—a better, more democratic tech future."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.a775b641-fa2c-4427-85f2-94183de7e024"
msgid "2025 Cohort: Making the invisible visible"
msgstr "2025 Cohort: Tornando o invisível visível"

msgctxt "body.a775b641-fa2c-4427-85f2-94183de7e024"
msgid "We believe that a better technology future is underpinned by infrastructure and systems that open and empower, not obscure."
msgstr "Acreditamos que um futuro tecnológico melhor se sustenta em infraestruturas e sistemas que sejam abertos e capacitadores, e não obscuros."

msgctxt "body.a775b641-fa2c-4427-85f2-94183de7e024"
msgid ""
"Imagine if developers could see exactly how their code affects the climate—and write cleaner software because of it. What if job seekers could understand why AI systems make hiring decisions—and "
"challenge unfair rejections? What if communities could predict pollution spikes before they happen—and take action to protect themselves?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.a775b641-fa2c-4427-85f2-94183de7e024"
msgid ""
"The breakthrough technologies that make this all possible are emerging. Early prototypes are proving the concept, communities are demanding access, and the potential for immense impact is clear. But"
" these technologies are stuck in the gap between \"proof of concept\" and \"ready for widespread use.”"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.a775b641-fa2c-4427-85f2-94183de7e024"
msgid ""
"Our inaugural Incubator cohort is helped four pioneering projects navigate this critical transition, building the pathways that put game-changing information directly into the hands of the people "
"who needed it most."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.48092ea9-7d2f-4e9d-aee7-71b54b509906.tabs.cc9c6dae-fad1-4524-b7d9-e76ffa2debe7.title"
